ArrayList internally use a dynamic array 
where as 
Linked List internally use Doubly Linked List

Manipulation with ArrayList is slow because lots of shifting internally need to be done
where as 
LinkedList is faster than ArrayList because it uses doubly linkked list


An ArrayList class act as a list only because it implements List interface
where as 
LinkedList class act as list an queue both

ArrayList is better for storing and accessing data
where 
LinkedList is better for manipulation